                </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="fs-2 text-body-emphasis">User Authentication</h3>
            <p>Securely register and manage your account. Log in to access personalized recommendations, manage your book listings, and connect with other book enthusiasts.</p>
            
          </div>
          <div class="feature col">
            <div class="feature-icon d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-bg-primary bg-gradient fs-2 mb-3">
